So here's the next one.

49:25.000 --> 49:29.000
It's probably the question that is maybe of greatest interest

49:29.000 --> 49:31.000
to the most people.

49:31.000 --> 49:35.000
And that is where does the inevitability end, right?

49:35.000 --> 49:38.000
So in your spectrum, you know,

49:38.000 --> 49:41.000
it would be a sort of rather disappointing take-home message

49:41.000 --> 49:44.000
of inevitable life was basically the inevitability

49:44.000 --> 49:46.000
of a bunch of small molecules.

49:46.000 --> 49:48.000
And so the question is,

49:48.000 --> 49:53.000
is there some possibility of identifying other regularities

49:53.000 --> 49:55.000
and other processes that would make

49:55.000 --> 49:59.000
more sophisticated, more complex structures inevitable too?

