So, for example, you know, we watched Star Trek

50:02.000 --> 50:06.000
and we encountered bipedal self-conscious extraterrestrials.

50:06.000 --> 50:09.000
Are we going to be forever disappointed

50:09.000 --> 50:12.000
and only ever encounter, you know, the Krebs cycle?

50:12.000 --> 50:14.000
Or is there something about the theory,

50:14.000 --> 50:16.000
or some theory that might be related to it,

50:16.000 --> 50:18.000
that would say that more complex structures

